 Byzantine province.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Greek, Modern (1453-).0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aAthen. 4aGriechisch-Orthodoxe Kirche. 4aMittelalter. 4aPolitik. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh1 aKolobu, Photeine Ch., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKolovou, Foteini, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI0 cprintz978311017166240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311087752640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110877526423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110877526/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014